"{\"uid\": \"americansongwriter.com-im-so-sorry-kelly-clarkson-reacts-to-breaking-down-during-celine-dions-paris-olympics-performance\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"By  Chris Piner  With millions of people watching around the world, Paris kicked off the 2024 Olympic Games with style.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 68, \"end\": 73, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5040479150349986e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout the opening ceremony, Paris showcased its rich history in art, expression, and music.\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 153, \"end\": 158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5040479150349986e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony featured performances by Lady Gaga, who dazzled for the cameras.\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And with the Eiffel Tower featuring a light display unlike any other, the opening ceremony was a massive success.\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 408, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But while viewers supported their home countries and favorite athletes, nothing compared to the finale of the ceremony whenCeline Dion's performance caused even Kelly Clarkson to break down.\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 570, \"end\": 584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although a powerhouse on the stage,Diontook a break from the spotlight to focus on her health.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Suffering from stiff person syndrome, the icon promised to fight the illness and eventually return to the stage.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 808, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And in true Dion fashion, her return was nothing short of historic.\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And for Clarkson, she not only watched the performance but felt it.\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 944, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 885, \"end\": 893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\", \"score\": 0.9999999978772394, \"rank\": 2.122157482391261e-09, \"text\": \"Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Besides holding back tears, Clarkson said, \\\"I can not speak.\\\"\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 973, \"end\": 981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\", \"score\": 0.9999999978772394, \"rank\": 2.122157482391261e-09, \"text\": \"Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaining some control, she added, \\\"I have been inspired.\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been dancing.\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was not ready for that ending.\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so sorry you looked at me and I was like, 'Wait.\\\"\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Dion put her illness behind her to officially start the Olympic Games, Clarkson insisted,\\u00a0\\\"This is her purpose.\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1250, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\", \"score\": 0.9999999978772394, \"rank\": 2.122157482391261e-09, \"text\": \"Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so sorry I am trying to hold it together.\\\"\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"[RELATED: Celine Dion's Eiffel Tower Performance at the Olympics Has Kelly Clarkson in Tears and Fans in a Frenzy]  It wasn't just Clarkson who felt the performance as even broadcaster Mike Tirico took a moment to soak in the performance, explaining,\\u00a0 \\\"C\\u00e9line Dion, who has been dealing with a rare progressive neurological disorder, and has not appeared very often, performing in public, with\\u2026 a performance fitting of this amazing night.\\\"\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1409, \"end\": 1423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\"}, {\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\", \"score\": 0.9999999978772394, \"rank\": 2.122157482391261e-09, \"text\": \"Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_C